Subject: Re: [VB] Leaky carb

I had a similar problem. What I did was buy a carb rebuild kit ($10) 
and replaced every seal, gasket and also the needle valve (comes with 
the kit). The leak is gone. It was a fairly easy fix (once I figured 
the problem out).

-Rocky

